> This solution introduces a new script phase in Xcode which handles Xcode's build-time variables and translates them into an appropriate cargo rustc command invocation. I would still need to update it with the latest changes on main and provide documentation on integrating the rust library into an Xcode project

I'm not really familiar with using Xcode, but at least from corrosions side it should also work in regular CMake builds with the XCode Generator, right?

